T02D2988:53b-0: @53b * // dpal rdo rje can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2988:53b-1: brjed byed kyi gdon las thar bar 'dod pas /
T02D2988:53b-3: mtshan ma shes par bya ste /
T02D2988:53b-4: mi drag cing khro gtum can la yar ngo'i tshes gnyis dang /
T02D2988:53b-8: mar ngo'i nyer dgu la snga dro dang srod la 'jug go //
T02D2988:53b-9: zhugs pa'i mtshan ma ni kha nas sbu bar skyug pa dang /
T02D2988:53b-13: lus sa la 'gyel ba rnams yin no //
T02D2988:53b-14: de las thar pa'i thabs ni dud pa dang /
T02D2988:54a-6: 'bras chan dang ldan pa'i gtor ma sbyin no //
T02D2988:54a-7: de nas de'i 'og tu nad pa khrus byas te /
T02D2988:54a-13: bil ba'i rtsa ba 'di dag cha bsnyams la /
T02D2988:54a-14: ra gcin dang lhan cig tu btags /
T02D2988:54a-15: mar phul bzhi dang ba gcin phul bcu drug gi
T02D2988:54a-16: nang du me chung bas btsos la snga ma bzhin
T02D2988:54a-17: du bsngags te sbyor ba byas pas thar nges so
